540
00:22:51,180 --> 00:22:51,520
Movement.

541
00:22:52,181 --> 00:22:54,262
Movement grabs the eye and the player's attention.

542
00:22:55,403 --> 00:22:56,784
This can be anything that fits your game.

543
00:22:56,924 --> 00:23:00,167
Big scripted moments, birds, sparks, buddies, enemies,

544
00:23:00,447 --> 00:23:02,889
and even just something flapping in the breeze.

545
00:23:04,570 --> 00:23:06,711
Also, make good use of the direction of the movement.

546
00:23:07,112 --> 00:23:08,673
