689
00:29:30,869 --> 00:29:33,550
A very brief and simple history of light

690
00:29:33,570 --> 00:29:35,371
might start with the sun, right?

691
00:29:35,451 --> 00:29:38,132
The sun is really great, let's give it up now for the sun.

692
00:29:38,913 --> 00:29:41,194
